snippet.title: Parkour Legends - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Parkour Legends is a 2D parkour game with air-tight controls, inspired by the thrill of movement and momentum in free running. Sprint, slide, roll, rebound, grab onto ledges, and run across walls to complete hundreds of hand-crafted courses as quickly and stylishly as possible to become the ultimate Parkour Legend. Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2115130/Parkour_Legends/?utm_source=yt-4
